Nithiarasu et al.\cite{nithiarasu1997natural} proposed a generalized N-S equation for isothermal incompressible fluid flow in porous media which can be expressed as follows:

text:
\begin{equation}
f_i(\textbf{x}+\textbf{e}_i \Delta t, t+ \Delta t)- f_i(\textbf{x},t) = -\frac{1}{\tau} [f_i(\textbf{x},t)-f_i^{eq}(\textbf{x},t)] +\Delta t \textit{F}_i,
